msgstr "从部署 JAR 中发现每个扩展的技能需要 Quarkus 3.35.0 以上版本。对于旧版本，代理将依赖于 `quarkus_searchDocs` 的指导。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Writing effective skills"
msgstr "有效的写作技巧"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Keep these principles in mind:"
msgstr "请牢记这些原则："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Be prescriptive, not descriptive.*\n"
"The agent does not need a tour of your API surface; it can read Javadoc for that.\n"
"It needs to know the _right_ pattern to use and the mistakes to avoid.\n"
"Instead of \"the `@Transactional` annotation can be used on methods,\" write \"always annotate write operations with `@Transactional`.\""
msgstr "*要规范，不要描述。* 代理不需要参观你的 API 表面；它可以阅读 Javadoc 来实现这一点。它需要知道 _正确的_ 使用模式和应避免的错误。与其写\" `@Transactional` 注解可用于方法\"，不如写 \"始终使用 `@Transactional` 对写操作进行注解\"。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Focus on what surprises people.*\n"
"If every new developer hits the same three issues with your extension, those belong in the skill.\n"
"If something works exactly as expected, you probably do not need to mention it."
msgstr "*关注让人惊喜的地方。* 如果每个新开发者都会在扩展中遇到同样的三个问题，那么这些问题就属于技能范畴。如果某些东西完全按照预期运行，你可能不需要提及。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Keep it concise.*\n"
"A skill that is 50 lines of actionable guidance beats 500 lines of documentation rehash.\n"
"The agent will search the full documentation via `quarkus_searchDocs` when it needs details.\n"
"The skill is for the patterns and pitfalls that documentation alone does not prevent."
msgstr "*简明扼要。* 50 行可操作指导的技能胜过 500 行的重复文档。代理需要详细资料时，会通过 `quarkus_searchDocs 搜索` 全部文档。该技能针对的是单靠文档无法避免的模式和陷阱。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Include testing patterns.*\n"
"How should tests be written for your extension?\n"
"What test infrastructure does it provide?\n"
"This is one of the areas where agents struggle most without guidance."
msgstr "*包括测试模式。* 应如何编写扩展测试？它提供了哪些测试基础设施？这是代理商在没有指导的情况下最头疼的问题之一。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Test with a cheap model.*\n"
"A large frontier model might produce correct code even without your skill.\n"
"The real test is whether a smaller, cheaper model (like Haiku or GPT-4o mini) gets it right when following your skill.\n"
"If it does, your skill is doing its job."
msgstr "*使用廉价模型进行测试。* 即使没有你的技能，大型前沿模型也可能生成正确的代码。真正的测试是一个更小、更便宜的模型（如 Haiku 或 GPT-4o mini）在使用你的技能时是否能生成正确的代码。如果正确，说明你的技能发挥了作用。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The three-layer composition system"
msgstr "三层构成系统"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Different teams have different conventions, and sometimes the built-in skill does not cover a specific use case.\n"
"To handle this, skills use a three-layer composition system:"
msgstr "不同的团队有不同的惯例，有时内置技能并不涵盖特定的用例。为了解决这个问题，技能使用了三层构成系统："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Extension skill**: ships with the extension itself (`META-INF/quarkus-skill.md`)"
msgstr "*扩展技能* ：与扩展本身一起发布 `（META-INF/quarkus-skill.md）`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**User-level skill**: stored at `~/.quarkus/skills/<extension-name>/SKILL.md`, applies to all projects for that developer"
msgstr "*用户级技能* ：存储在 `~/.quarkus/skills/< 扩展名>/SKILL.md` ，适用于该开发者的所有项目。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Project-level skill**: stored at `.agent/skills/<extension-name>/SKILL.md`, applies to one project only"
msgstr "*项目级技能* ：存储在 `.agent/skills/<extension-name>/SKILL.md` 中，仅适用于一个项目"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Layers 1 and 2 support *enhance* (append additional guidance) and *override* (fully replace) composition, controlled by the `mode` field in the SKILL.md frontmatter:"
msgstr "第 1 层和第 2 层支持 *增强* （附加额外指导）和 *覆盖* （完全替换）成分，由 SKILL.md 前置文件中的 `模式` 字段控制："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Project-level skills (layer 3) are standalone files read as-is, with no composition against the base layers.\n"
"This means any agent can read them directly from the filesystem without needing to understand the composition chain.\n"
"Use the `quarkus_saveSkill` tool to materialize a fully composed skill into `.agent/skills/`, then edit the file directly to customize it for your project."
msgstr "项目级技能（第 3 层）是按原样读取的独立文件，与基础层没有任何关联。这意味着任何代理都可以直接从文件系统中读取它们，而无需了解组成链。使用 `quarkus_saveSkill` 工具可将一个完全组成的技能实体化为 `.agent/skills/` ，然后直接编辑该文件，为你的项目进行定制。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For global customizations that apply across all projects, the agent can use `quarkus_updateSkill` to write to `~/.quarkus/skills/`."
msgstr "对于适用于所有项目的全局定制，代理可以使用 `quarkus_updateSkill` 写入 `~/.quarkus/skills/。`"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Privacy"
msgstr "隐私权"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus Agent MCP runs entirely on your machine.\n"
"It does not collect telemetry or send data to any third party.\n"
"Outbound network requests are limited to downloading extension JARs from Maven Central, pulling pre-indexed documentation containers, and checking for Quarkus version updates. Everything is cached locally after the first use."
msgstr "Quarkus Agent MCP 完全在你的机器上运行。它不会收集遥测数据，也不会向任何第三方发送数据。对外网络请求仅限于从 Maven Central 下载扩展 JAR、提取预索引文档容器以及检查 Quarkus 版本更新。首次使用后，所有请求都会缓存在本地。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What is next"
msgstr "下一步是什么"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus Agent MCP is part of the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/53093[DevStar working group] and we are actively developing new capabilities.\n"
"If you are an extension author interested in shipping skills, or a developer with feedback on the workflow, we want to hear from you."
msgstr "Quarkus Agent MCP 是 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/53093[DevStar 工作组] 的一部分，我们正在积极开发新功能。如果您是对发布技能感兴趣的扩展作者，或者是对工作流程有反馈意见的开发人员，我们希望收到您的来信。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Try it out:"
msgstr "试试吧"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This example uses Claude Code, but any coding agent that supports the MCP protocol (Cursor, Windsurf, GitHub Copilot, JetBrains AI, and others) can connect to Quarkus Agent MCP. See the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-agent-mcp[README] for configuration instructions for each agent."
msgstr "本示例使用了克劳德代码，但任何支持 MCP 协议的编码代理（Cursor、Windsurf、GitHub Copilot、JetBrains AI 等）都可以连接到 Quarkus Agent MCP。有关每个代理的配置说明，请参阅 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-agent-mcp[README] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
